snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play Halloween Trick or Treat Candy Haul
snippet.description:
Diana Pretend Play Halloween trick or treating for candy haul. The little girl knocks on the door and says “Trick or Treat!”. Doors open hosts dressed in terrifying costumes. Diana was scared, but she was brave girl and gathered a lot of candy! Happy Halloween!...
